<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Pre-Requisites - LifeNest</title>

  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-top: 80px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 30px 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #d9534f;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    ul li {
      background: #f8d7da;
      color: #721c24;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out;
    }

    ul li:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
      background: #f5c6cb;
    }

    .btn-back {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      background: #d9534f;
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .btn-back:hover {
      background: #c9302c;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .text-center {
      text-align: center;
    }

    i {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Pre-Requisites for Blood Donation</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Donor must be between 18 and 65 years of age.</li>
      <li>Donor should weigh at least 50 kg.</li>
      <li>Ensure you are well-hydrated before donating blood.</li>
      <li>Avoid alcohol or smoking 24 hours before donation.</li>
      <li>Eat a light, healthy meal before donating.</li>
      <li>No donation if you had major surgery in the last 6 months.</li>
      <li>Minimum 3-month gap between donations.</li>
    </ul>

    
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
